{"tid":2122552,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"DSE放榜 國安法壓境政權屢向教育伸手 考生海外升學為移民鋪路 海外發展處處理機遇","createTime":"2020-07-24T05:11:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T18:52:25.000Z","uid":248054,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d8c051158c3cc34db148d87fb7aaeb78f20a4c6d","tid":2122552,"uid":248054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T05:11:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200722/YX3MXICWR5XTDDWQOWCS2PIIQI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200722%2FYX3MXICWR5XTDDWQOWCS2PIIQI%2F&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6GZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=01f0871a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200722%2FYX3MXICWR5XTDDWQOWCS2PIIQI%2F&h=f6c3613f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200722/YX3MXICWR5XTDDWQOWCS2PIIQI/</a><br />\n<br />\n在武漢肺炎第三波疫情爆發下，一年一度的中學文憑試今日放榜。有海外升學中心今早7點公佈DSE後明顯多考生前往報名。有報讀海外課程的同學直言，香港政局令人心灰意冷，惟有為更好的將來謀定後路。<br />\n<br />\n中學文憑試今終於揭曉，在海外升學中心展覽中有不少應屆考生前來報名海外升學，但礙於限聚令需分時段分批入場。<br />\n<br />\n博華海外升學中心總經理鄺煒立接受《蘋果》訪問時表示，今年報名海外升學人數較往年多出20%，有成績較好的學生亦有前來報名，「（放榜後）今日有約30多名登記入場報讀海外大學」；大多報讀海外考生已不再考慮本地課程，「見到學生心態唔同咗好多，有好多學生直頭唔等DSE成績已先預留位置&hellip;&hellip;都會見到有啲唔等Jupus放榜直接想出國讀書」。<br />\n<br />\n鄺續指，今年澳洲、英國等放寬了留學條件，包括放寬收生成績要求，並更積極收生，變相令升讀海外學生人數較往年多。<br />\n<br />\n今年文憑試考生先後歷經送中惡法纏繞，又有「港版國安法」壓境，本港局勢的不明朗，令有不少應屆考生選擇海外升學。<br />\n<br />\n已分別報讀英國及澳洲課程的何同學指，外國讀書環境較好，而「今年有社運，有較多煩心事」，故希望海外升學。同時，何又指，最想報讀的國家是英國，「想為之後嘅移民鋪路，想為理想嘅生活環境而（計劃）升學」。<br />\n<br />\n陳同學打算到澳洲留學，「始終香港社會狀況唔平穩，又有《國安法》等唔同政治因素」，故想到外國升學想為將來打算。陪同女兒報讀海外課程的陳先生指，由教育局DQ歷史科題目事件開始已對香港將來感到灰心，「在社會運動（開始）&hellip;&hellip;對香港教育制度太失望、對所有（香港將來）都失望」，「未來是首要為子女下一代」，故為女兒計劃好將來。"},{"pid":"c882527333fa41b8d5df18efd3fd83e45ad17180","tid":2122552,"uid":225931,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T05:17:37.000Z","msg":"香港人才流失嘅開始"},{"pid":"7587c304affa437b84d84b8310521391d012daaf","tid":2122552,"uid":302831,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T05:21:48.000Z","msg":"正常有家底嘅都會咁走 <br />\n讀完書就順便移埋民"},{"pid":"810f6677d962720419cf4062662e85799cbd69a5","tid":2122552,"uid":248054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7587c304affa437b84d84b8310521391d012daaf","tid":2122552,"uid":302831,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T05:21:48.000Z","msg":"正常有家底嘅都會咁走 <br />\n讀完書就順便移埋民"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T14:25:10.000Z","msg":"真啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54f1564a21efefed8dd1e1c11cd6c9e83bec939b","tid":2122552,"uid":248054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T14:32:40.000Z","msg":"clearance round尚未結束<br />\n真心可以考慮英國讀書"},{"pid":"79436814a6ee824415fa0c0b310cc61c07fbc81d","tid":2122552,"uid":6122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T04:49:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7efcecb9edb1d135b0f38c094898208078ae20c","tid":2122552,"uid":248054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79436814a6ee824415fa0c0b310cc61c07fbc81d","tid":2122552,"uid":6122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T04:49:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T05:46:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8407f45f5ece680b8d70f896e5a70a7de1f8b140","tid":2122552,"uid":231886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7587c304affa437b84d84b8310521391d012daaf","tid":2122552,"uid":302831,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T05:21:48.000Z","msg":"正常有家底嘅都會咁走 <br />\n讀完書就順便移埋民"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T15:28:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2141510/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2141510/page/1</a><br />\n[整合] 中大湯宿傳銷狗<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">幫手推，要推到傳銷狗仆街</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"b37cb43957aaf4bcc0f2d0bb44ad7b11008f13c2","tid":2122552,"uid":6122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7efcecb9edb1d135b0f38c094898208078ae20c","tid":2122552,"uid":248054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79436814a6ee824415fa0c0b310cc61c07fbc81d","tid":2122552,"uid":6122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T04:49:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T05:46:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T17:06:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a43159047d38ee4334458ec72ce781873e3dd696","tid":2122552,"uid":363481,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T18:52:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}